name: wigglesphere
description: It's a sphere. It wiggles. It loops. It looks like a .gif but it's not, it's a png. It looks like a sphere, but it's not, it's a circle (duh). It looks like it wiggles, but is that really wiggling? More like waving... It's got sexy fidelity because it's a png. It's got more than 1 bit of transparency because it's a png. It entices you to stare at it forever and ever.
